Recently asked one of the questions related to JWT token and multiple logins

Suppose a user logs into the same web application from two different machines at the same time.
1. What happens to their JWT token or session?
2. Will both tokens remain valid?
Or will the first one automatically expire or get revoked?
How can we design the system to acheive this?

